en_6227288_0	COLOMBO (News 1st) – The Department of Excise noted that all bars across the island should remain closed today (February 04) due to the Independence Day celebrations.
en_6227288_1	Media Spokesperson for the Department and Deputy Commissioner of Excise Kapila Kumarasinghe said that an island-wide operation is in effect to track down those who do not comply with this order.
